column2:
"Oh, <%me>, do you have a
minute? I wanted to ask you to join
me on a client order."

"It seems like Zeno needs some time to
himself, and I totally get that."

"But with me being who I am, I get all worried
when I'm on my own. I feel so much better
if there's somebody else with me."

"Whenever you have some spare time,
I would really appreciate it. Thanks!"

"あ、<%me>
ちょっといいかな？
よければ、あたしの依頼に付き合って？"

"ゼノはしばらく一人になりたいみたい。
そういうのは尊重したいから、さ。"

"でもほら、あたしってこんなんだし
一人だと不安だからさ。
きみが一緒だと安心かな、って。"

"暇なときで構わないから
よろしくお願い。"
